<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-view-transactions-bet-history">How to view transactions &amp; bet history</h3>
<h4 id="how-to-view-my-transactions">How to view my transactions</h4>
<ol>
<li>Log into your account and click on &quot;My Bets&quot; on the bottom-right corner.</li>
<li>Go to &quot;Transactions&quot; option to view transaction details.</li>
<li><p>Select the desired transaction category from the drop-down column on the top-left corner.</p>
<p> <img src="../../../../assets/app-transaction-history.png" alt=""></p>
</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="how-to-view-my-bets">How to view my bets</h4>
<ol>
<li>Log into your account and click on &quot;Me&quot;.</li>
<li>To see sports bets, click on &quot;SPORTS BET HISTORY&quot; highligted in green.</li>
</ol>
</div>